QuestData.Title: Holed Up
QuestData.Description:
I can't believe you made it here!
I don't know how much longer I could have stayed hidden in here.$B$BI'm sure that there are others. $C, we have to rescue them! Then we can go to Shado-Pan Fallback. The master there will know what to do!
QuestData.LogDescription: Rescue Jin Warmkeg, Ya Firebough, Old Lady Fung, and Sya Zhong.
QuestData.RewardText: We didn't know that there were any survivors out there.$B$BThank you for bringing them to safety, $n.
